Company Overview of Epic Ventures Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Epic Ventures Inc., doing business as Epic Wines, Ltd., operates as an importer and wholesale distributor of wines and distilled spirits. It offers products through sales representatives in northern and southern California. The company was founded in 1995 and is based in Aptos, California.


